&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate documentation and regulatory compliance requirements associated with ECM and related programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support quality, utilization, and member outcome goals established by the organization and health plan partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
