&lt;p&gt;The primary focus of this role is establishing a scalable, durable data platform. This includes laying the groundwork for longer-term initiatives such as the longitudinal patient record, population-level analytics, and product instrumentation. You will partner closely with Engineering and Product to ensure the data platform supports roadmap priorities and outcome measurement as the company grows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position reports to the &lt;strong&gt;Principal Data Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; and partners closely with Engineering and Product.&lt;/p&gt;
