&lt;li&gt;Establish data quality, testing, and monitoring practices that make pipelines reliable and trustworthy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help shape ingestion patterns and architecture standards alongside the Principal Data Engineer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable company-wide metrics for care outcomes and operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional leads to develop and iterate on a suite of core operational dashboards, ensuring teams have the self-service tools they need to track company metrics and outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
