&lt;li&gt;Set clear expectations for performance, productivity, and team management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hold managers accountable for outcomes, coaching, and corrective action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistent management practices across geographies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
